---
title: "_getAssetOutAmount (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_clamp: elapsedTime = min(elapsedTime, auctionDuration)
    q_clamp --> q_multiplier: compute priceMultiplier via linear decay
    q_multiplier --> q_get_out_price: priceMultiplier = startingPriceMultiplier - (startingPM - endingPM) * elapsedTime / auctionDuration
    q_get_out_price --> q_usd_value: assetOutUsdPrice = _getAssetPrice(s_assetOut)
    q_usd_value --> q_convert: auctionUsdValue = amountIn * assetInUsdPrice / 10**decimals * priceMultiplier (round up)
    q_convert --> [*]: return auctionUsdValue * 10**assetOutDecimals / assetOutUsdPrice (round up)

    note right of q_multiplier
        INV-001: priceMultiplier decreases linearly from startingPriceMultiplier to endingPriceMultiplier
        INV-002: elapsedTime is clamped to auctionDuration (no extra decay past end)
        INV-003: mulDivUp and mulWadUp ensure rounding favors the protocol (bidder pays more)
    end note
